OL,3,CNewcastle University faces #35m
OL,4,Cblackhole as international students
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FA decline in the number of
OL,8,Finternational students at Newcastle
OL,9,FUniversity will leave a #35 million
OL,10,Fshortfall in their budget, according
OL,11,Fto an email sent to staff.
OL,13,FThe university's vice chancellor
OL,14,FProfessor Chris Day told staff that
OL,15,Fthere will be immediate cost cutting
OL,16,Fmeasures which include a freeze on
OL,17,Fchanges to existing contracts,
OL,18,Fincluding requests for longer working
OL,19,Fhours.
