OL,7,FReviews are also underway for the
OL,8,Fannual staff pay review and academic
OL,9,Fpromotions.
OL,11,FIn the email, seen by the Local
OL,12,FDemocracy Reporting Service, Prof Day
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our aim is to protect core
OL,14,Feducation and research while
OL,15,Facknowledging that immediate cost
OL,16,Fcontrols will require difficult
OL,17,Fchoices and prioritisation".
