OL,7,FHe said Newcastle University had
OL,8,Falready built in #15 million of
OL,9,F"mitigations" in its annual budget,
OL,10,Fbut must now find an additional #20m
OL,11,Fin savings to avoid a financial
OL,12,Fdeficit.
OL,14,FAccording to the email, Newcastle
OL,15,FUniversity's Executive Board has
OL,16,Fagreed to freeze recruitment to all
OL,17,Fnew and replacement "core funded"
OL,18,Fposts until further notice.
