OL,7,FA Newcastle University spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are in a sound financial
OL,9,Fposition but like many other
OL,10,Funiversities, we are managing the
OL,11,Fimpact of a shortfall in international
OL,12,Fstudent recruitment this year
OL,13,Fresulting in a fall in income.
OL,15,F"We are implementing cost-control
OL,16,Fmeasures which will allow us to
OL,17,Fprotect our core business and
OL,18,Fstrengthen our financial resilience."
