OL,7,FAccording to Home Office figures,
OL,8,Fstudent visa applications between
OL,9,FJanuary and August this year, 278,700,
OL,10,Fwere 17% lower than in January to
OL,11,FAugust 2023.
OL,13,FThis follows government changes in
OL,14,FJanuary 2024 meaning most students are
OL,15,Fno longer allowed to bring dependents
OL,16,Fwith them.
