OL,3,CNewcastle University faces #35m
OL,4,Cblackhole as international students
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FIn February this year, Northumbria
OL,8,FUniversity announced it would slash
OL,9,Fits staffing budget by #12.5m. A move
OL,10,Fwhich the University claimed was also
OL,11,Fattributed to difficulty with
OL,12,Finternational recruitment as well as
OL,13,Fhigher than normal energy prices.
OL,15,FThe budget cut was dubbed a "crisis"
OL,16,Fby the university's chapter of the
OL,17,FUniversity and College Union. The fall
OL,18,Fin international student applications
OL,19,Fwas estimated to cost the university
OL,20,F#10m in lost income.
